phoenix
phoenix-spark整合失败

hbase-spark整合失败
可以在spark shell中读取hbase信息
idea中导入hbase和spark依赖包冲突,无法导入相关类

```scala
a.saveToPhoenix(
      "STEAMING_RECORD",
      Seq("ID", "TIME", "RECORDCOUNT", "RECORDTYPE", "CREATED_TIME"),
      zkUrl = Some("localhost:2181")
    )
```
